<div style="background-color:#7c7c7c; color:white; padding:20px; font-size:22px; margin-left:20px;">8. BOOKING CANCELLATION</div>

<div style="background-color:#b8b8b8; color:white; padding:20px; font-size:22px; margin-left:20px; line-height:150%;">How do I cancel a booking?</div>
<p style="padding:0px 20px 0px 40px;">The QVC Reservation Cancellation Policy is as follows: Cancellation of, or changes to confirmed bookings will be accepted for the period up to 6 (six) weeks prior to the due occupation date of the confirmed booking, subject to payment of a reasonable administrative Cancellation Fee.<br /><br />
Cancellations of a booking within the 6 week period prior to the due occupation date, can either be substituted for an available alternative resort, subject to the payment of a cancellation fee, or alternatively the member may forfeit the Usage Units relative to the cancelled booking..</p>